BILLS KHAKIS
It's an ages old cliche that "they just don't make 'em like they used to." To the folks at Bills Khakis, it's at the very core of every piece of clothing they create. With inspiration taken from a pair of World War II era military khakis and the idea that quality is the most important element to any piece of clothing, Bills Khakis has become one of the most well-respected mens clothing brands in America. At PatrickJames.com you can get Bills Khakis sale priced, offering high-quality clothing at appealing prices.




